{"id":176140,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/global-voices-利比亚：人民的期望与担忧/","date":"2011-09-01T00:23:37Z","modified":"2011-09-01T00:23:37Z","title":"Global Voices | 利比亚：人民的期望与担忧","content":"<p><p>当利比亚革命人士逐渐逼近首都的黎波里时，人民在推特上表述他们的担忧和期望，这里是今晚推特上的部份谈话。</p>\n<p>Gheblawi说道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Gheblawi/status/104302756457758720\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Gheblawi/status/104302756457758720\">@Gheblawi</a>：我无法驳斥某些人的末日论，因为#的黎波里让我心烦意乱。让我们保持乐观并期望一切尽早结束。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/676403/inside-benghazi-free-libyan-army-training-camp\"><img title=\"Volunteers at Free Libyan Army training camp in Benghazi learn how to use weapons. \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Libya-rebels-advance-375x279.jpg\" alt=\"Volunteers at Free Libyan Army training camp in Benghazi learn how to use weapons. Image by Tomasz Grzyb, copyright Demotix (27/04/2011).\" width=\"375\" height=\"279\" /></a></p>\n<p>志愿者在班加西利比亚解放军训练营学习如何使用武器。图像来自Tomasz Grzyb，版权属Demotix所有（2011年4月27日）</p>\n</div>\n<p>他之前在推特提到：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Gheblawi/status/104260211128270848\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Gheblawi/status/104260211128270848\">@Gheblawi</a>：数分钟前和#的黎波里的家人通话，他们的地区自从昨夜电力时有时无，父亲毫不屈服，精神高昂#利比亚</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>ChangeInLibya</em>补充说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search/realtime/Tripoli\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search/realtime/Tripoli\">@ChangeInLibya</a>：@Gheblawi这里也是一样，我先前和我母亲通话，她相当担心我们的家人困在的黎波里..rabbi yester（愿主保佑）</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>Armchair Arab</em>回应：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/ArmchairArab/status/104303941864529920\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/ArmchairArab/status/104303941864529920\">@ArmchairArab</a>：@Gheblawi @ChangeInLibya我多数的家人也在的黎波里，我每晚都有打电话给他们，他们似乎精神高昂。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>Libya United</em>以乐观的态度加入谈话。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Libya_United/status/104304276557402113\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Libya_United/status/104304276557402113\">@Libya_United</a>：@ChangeInLibya @Gheblawi我的亲人没有一个离开的黎波里。朋友们要保持乐观，混局是无可避免的，但我相信这很快就会结束了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>Nadia Maddox</em>抱着类似的希望，她说道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/NadiaMaddox/status/104304349227913216\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/NadiaMaddox/status/104304349227913216\">@NadiaMaddox</a>：@FromJoanne @Gheblawi我的父母和其他亲人也在的黎波里 :( 希望它尽早结束而并不会太残暴。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>同时，Nusaiba的表述较为焦虑，她说道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/QdiyatnaAlhuria/status/104301663258558464\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/QdiyatnaAlhuria/status/104301663258558464\">@QdiyatnaAlhuria</a>（我们的目的是为了我们的自由）：#最遭的感受就是无法得知你家人朋友的情况会怎么样，而且无法就近照应。#的黎波里 #Tajoura</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>但Mariam Addarrat相当振奋鼓舞：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Ummustafa78/status/104304642611101696\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Ummustafa78/status/104304642611101696\">@Ummustafa78</a>：@Gheblawi @ChangeInLibya 格达费（Muammar Gaddafi）向来都是到最后一刻才谈判，我希望自由斗士来到的黎波里的城门时他会离开。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>最后<em>Libya TV</em>总结：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/libyatv/status/104304484955602944\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/libyatv/status/104304484955602944\">@libyatv</a>：@Gheblawi 这只是对局势的不确定性所造成的，但格达费将不会在的黎波里，他将不再逗留于利比亚，当然这是必然的事！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/amira-al-hussaini/\" title=\"文章导读 Amira Al Hussaini\">Amira Al Hussaini</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/tina/\" title=\"文章导读 Tina Campling\">Tina Campling</a> </span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/18/libya-anxiety-and-hope-as-revolutionaries-edge-their-way-to-tripoli/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/09/01/9734/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F01%2F9734%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F01%2F9734%2F&#038;desc=%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F01%2F9734%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F01%2F9734%2F&#038;text=%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F01%2F9734%2F&#038;title=%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</sp